dcterms:description: The dataset produced by MELVIN consists of 7,853,853 different setups of which 1,638,233 samples are labeled positive. Each setup consists of a sequence of optical elements, and the two target values are entanglement classification and Schmidt rank vector.
dcterms:title: Dataset produced by MELVIN
